data.description: Nestled on a sprawling 4.86-acre plot just off CR-78 in Labelle Florida, this 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom modular home is ready for its new owner. Brand NEW ROOF, Additional structures and a peaceful location. There has been significant Water Damage to the home, and work still needs to be done. But with the New Roof and some TLC from a new Owner, the Large Home could be a wonderful asset to this property. In addition to the spacious residence, you'll find three greenhouse structures and two 40ft storage containers and one out-building that's perfect for your gardening projects, tools, and toys. PVC pipe throughout the property(once used for irrigation) allows for agricultural usage as this property was once a thriving Hibiscus farm.
